  <section slot="overview">
    <h1>Corporate Team Building Candle Making - Centerville, TN</h1>
    <p>Looking for innovative corporate team building? Bring your team together for a professional candle-making experience that fosters collaboration, creativity, and team bonding. This hands-on activity provides the perfect environment for teams to connect outside the traditional office setting.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>This is team building through creative collaboration. Your team will learn professional candle-making techniques, select premium scents, and create custom candles in a professional yet relaxed atmosphere. The process encourages communication, creativity, and teamwork—perfect for strengthening professional relationships.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>All professional candle-making materials</li>
      <li>Premium container selection</li>
      <li>Wide variety of high-quality scents</li>
      <li>Expert facilitation and instruction</li>
      <li>Professional team-building atmosphere</li>
      <li>Take-home custom candles as team mementos</li>
      <li>Optional: Refreshments and group photos</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Corporate team building events</li>
      <li>Department retreats and outings</li>
      <li>New employee orientation activities</li>
      <li>Executive team bonding</li>
      <li>Remote teams meeting face-to-face</li>
      <li>Professional development programs</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and professional team introductions (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Candle-making instruction and safety overview (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Container and scent selection (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Collaborative candle creation (60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Team sharing and professional photos (20 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $25-35 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 5-30 team members (larger groups available)<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> No experience required
    </p>

